column5: have a garmin76csx unit. do they have a chip for lac des milles lacs? havent fish this body of water for about 8 years. how has the fishing been in recent years? walleye and pike bigger since the new slot..its cold in chicago today.gonna be a long winter.look forward to your responses ...jig out!!!
